der g- hoypt-&lt;tlien&gt; fun Vilner geto iz geven FRANZ MURER,

24
00:01:29,770 --> 00:01:32,973
der shtel-fartrater, &lt;farshtreter&gt; fun GEBIETSKOMMISSAR,

25
00:01:32,973 --> 00:01:33,847
HINGSTn,

26
