00:01:37,313 --> 00:01:40,617
oyf velkhn's gevisn s'iz iber hundert toyznt mentshn.

30
00:01:40,789 --> 00:01:44,647
MURER, s'iz nito keyn mentsh fun Vilne velkher zol nit visn, ver &lt;dos&gt; iz geven MURER.

31
00:01:45,970 --> 00:01:48,917
MURER aleyn iz geshtanen baym toyer. ye, hot men gezogt

32
00:01:49,058 --> 00:01:52,680
az biz fir in der fri darf vern geendikt di registratsye,

33
00:01:53,226 --> 00:01:55,245
un &lt;nokh&gt; dan darfn di,

34
00:01:55,302 --> 00:01:57,456
, INHABER fun geln shayn

35
00:01:57,546 --> 00:01:59,649
mit di tsugeshribene,

36
00:02:00,060 --> 00:02:03,108
 dos heyst, di ofitsyel derloybene

37
00:02:03,216 --> 00:02:04,849
familye-mitglider,

38
00:02:04,849 --> 00:02:06,444
kinder oder man-un-vayb,

39
00:02:06,444 --> 00:02:09,937
aroysgeyn tsu der arbet, dortn vu yeder arbet,

40
00:02:09,937 --> 00:02:12,035
un zitsn dortn dray mes-les.

41
00:02:12,936 --> 00:02:16,382
un far der tsayt hot men di geto gereynikt.

42
00:02:16,530 --> 00:02:18,633
do iz bay mir do a fotografye,

43
00:02:19,045 --> 00:02:23,100
di k- moment fun kontrol, ven es shteyen di daytshn un kontrolirn

44
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:27,847
az es zol kholile nit aroysgeyn a mentsh vos hot nit dem geln shayn oder d- mit di bloye numern.

45
00:02:29,068 --> 00:02:31,711
in der tsayt ven mir zaynen geshtanen baym toyer,

46
00:02:31,954 --> 00:02:34,462
MURER aleyn hot kontrolirt, nit nor er aleyn.

47
00:02:34,772 --> 00:02:38,497
dortn zet zikh oyf di fotografye a geto-politsist. er shteyt oykh mit a,

48
00:02:38,497 --> 00:02:40,145
a bloy-vays, aza min,

49
00:02:40,145 --> 00:02:41,988
oyfn, a pasik oyfn arbl.

50
00:02:42,906 --> 00:02:45,127
in der tsayt ven mir zaynen tsugegangen,

51
00:02:46,793 --> 00:02:48,640
ho- iz ge- k- for undz,

52
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:51,506
aza bisl on a zayt. azoy, ikh hob dos gezen ot,

53
00:02:51,563 --> 00:02:54,830
ot kimat azoy vi ikh sh- vi ikh ze aykh itster, azoy noent.

54
00:02:55,798 --> 00:02:57,682
iz tsugegangen a yunge meydl,

55
00:02:57,682 --> 00:03:01,971
a sheyne, a sheyne meydl, v- kh'gedenk, mit lange hor azelkhe, a, a,

56
00:03:01,971 --> 00:03:05,023
a tipish yidishe aza min, a kheynevdike.

57
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:08,010
un zi hot geshlept far di hent ire eltern.

58
00:03:08,202 --> 00:03:11,143
zi hot nit tsugeshribn keyn man, zi hot nit tsugeshribn keyn vayb, vayle

59
00:03:11,143 --> 00:03:15,822
es iz geven, di nakht iz geven a shreklekhe. mentshn vos hobn nit gehat hobn gebe-, keyn

60
00:03:15,822 --> 00:03:17,235
geln shayn hobn gebetn

61
00:03:17,235 --> 00:03:21,945
bay, bay, bay shkheynim, bay bakante, "rateve di kinder. shrayb tsu az s'iz di... kinder."

62
00:03:21,945 --> 00:03:23,982
tsushraybn iz geven nit-shver, vayle

63
00:03:23,982 --> 00:03:27,461
in geto hot men geyogt far finf minut. keyner &lt;hot&gt; keyn dokumentn nit gehat.

64
00:03:27,461 --> 00:03:28,969
iz zog on s'iz dayn kind.

65
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:31,182
s'iz geven bay undz a shokhnte.

66
00:03:31,182 --> 00:03:35,246
hot der, a shokhn hot tsugeshribn di, di tokhter

67
00:03:35,370 --> 00:03:36,714
als a vayb,

68
00:03:37,092 --> 00:03:40,680
un zayn vayb, dos heyst di tokhter's muter iz geblibn,

69
00:03:41,192 --> 00:03:44,407
visndik az m'vet ir dershisn, nor me darf rateven di tokhter.

70
00:03:44,483 --> 00:03:48,217
a yunger-man hot tsugeshribn zayn mamen als a vayb, un di mame hot zikh ge-

71
00:03:48,217 --> 00:03:52,863
gezen azoy zi zol oyszen, zikh tsuputsn, oyszen a bisl yinger. di tragedyes iz geven shreklekhe.

72
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:54,804
un di meydl hot, vayzt oys,

73
00:03:54,945 --> 00:03:59,138
 bash- &lt;m- m-&gt; nit gevelt, &lt;gez- iz zi&gt;, keyn man hot zi nit, keyn kinder hot zi nit,

74
00:03:59,138 --> 00:04:01,824
iz hot zi gemeynt az zi hot rekht tsu rateven di eltern,

75
00:04:01,864 --> 00:04:05,455
un zi vayzt im, ot dos, der f- d- dem geln shayn MURERn.

76
00:04:05,455 --> 00:04:09,244
zi vayzt im az dos iz mayne eltern. zi derklert im az zi hot mer keynem nit,

77
00:04:09,244 --> 00:04:10,526
un er shtupt zey op.

78
00:04:10,526 --> 00:04:15,504
di vos m'hot, er flegt brakirn oyb er flegt zen, umgefer, m'hot kinder gemegt biz zibetsn yor.

79
00:04:15,504 --> 00:04:18,077
un oyb me flegt ts- nu, mayn shvester iz geven

80
00:04:18,077 --> 00:04:24,411
akhtsn shoyn, iz, hot zi oysgezen vi zibetsn; nit, nit azoy shreklekh. nor ven &lt;me, antkegn&gt; a tsvantsik oder tsvey un tsvantsik yor,

81
00:04:24,411 --> 00:04:27,123
hot er dokh gezen s'iz a lign. oder az an alte mame

82
00:04:27,123 --> 00:04:28,678
geyt als, als a vayb.

83
00:04:28,678 --> 00:04:32,166
iz di flegt er, dortn &lt;ot ersht&gt; mm oyf Rudnitsker gas oykh,

84
00:04:32,166 --> 00:04:35,608
bay a toyer op- opgetribn. dos hot er dos, oysbrakirt.

85
00:04:35,631 --> 00:04:37,509
hot er a shtup geton di eltern

86
00:04:37,509 --> 00:04:38,336
ahin.

87
00:04:38,336 --> 00:04:39,509
hot zi zey mit

88
00:04:39,509 --> 00:04:43,218
koyekh vider aroysgerisn. zi vil, zi vil mit koyekh zikh durkhraysn.

89
00:04:43,292 --> 00:04:47,963
hot er zey a ts- a shtup geton, aroysegetr- -shlept dem pistolet, un ir oysgeshosn.

90
00:04:47,963 --> 00:04:49,614
un zi iz anidergefaln

91
00:04:49,738 --> 00:04:51,238
bay di fis fun di eltern.

92
00:04:51,238 --> 00:04:52,295
dos hob ikh aleyn gezen.

93
00:04:52,295 --> 00:04:53,955
s'iz geven in oktober eyn un fertsik.

94
00:04:54,278 --> 00:04:57,242
di azoy gerufene ershte aktsye fun di gele lates.

95
00:04:57,552 --> 00:05:02,001
dray mes-les zaynen mir opgezesn dortn oyfn hoyf fun di fabrik vu mame hot gearbet.

96
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:07,789
az mir hobn zikh umgekert in geto iz di geto geven a puste.

97
00:05:08,571 --> 00:05:13,149
in geto zaynen geven a sakh malines. nu, malines, dos heyst iber hoypt

98
00:05:13,149 --> 00:05:16,971
&lt;ganeyvim&gt; rufn malines vu zey, nor in geto hot geheysn malines,

99
00:05:16,971 --> 00:05:21,187
umgefer, s'iz geven a tsimer farshtelt mit a shaf oder mit a altn bufet,

100
00:05:21,244 --> 00:05:23,991
tsugeklapt tsum vant, araynkrikhn dortn durkh,

101
00:05:23,991 --> 00:05:27,096
durkh a politse durkh a untershte, un hintn zitsn mentshn

102
00:05:27,096 --> 00:05:28,005
bahaltn.

103
00:05:28,078 --> 00:05:32,386
ober di soldatn hobn dos altsding gevust. zey hobn &lt;he-&gt; flegn oysklapn di tirn,

104
00:05:32,386 --> 00:05:34,142
zey flegn oys- oyfraysn.

105
00:05:34,142 --> 00:05:37,540
mentshn hobn zikh gestarevet, umgefer, in bufet avekshteln a fleshl

106
00:05:37,540 --> 00:05:38,399
bronfn.

107
00:05:38,490 --> 00:05:42,365
az zey veln derzen di bronfn veln zey nemen, onheybn tsu trinken, efsher veln zey fargesn.

108
00:05:42,557 --> 00:05:47,886
s'iz geven, s- nokh dem iz geven, shpeter. dos iz geven, fun dest vegn, harbst eyn un fertsik.

109
00:05:47,886 --> 00:05:50,924
shpeter zaynen geven mer rafinirte malines.

110
00:05:50,924 --> 00:05:52,695
umgefer, s'iz geven gemakht

111
00:05:52,695 --> 00:05:53,570
a oyvn,

112
00:05:54,117 --> 00:05:56,963
un der oyvn dreyt zikh op un dortn untn iz a keler.

113
00:05:56,968 --> 00:05:59,100
nor dos hot veynik vemen geratevet.

114
00:05:59,100 --> 00:06:04,405
un az mir zaynen gekumen in undzer dire iz oykh geven aza min maline, ober keyner iz nit geven shoyn.

115
00:06:04,545 --> 00:06:07,154
es ken zayn az &lt;s'hot&gt; zikh funandergeveynt a kind.

116
00:06:07,482 --> 00:06:11,019
es ken zayn az zey hobn aleyn derzen. s'ken zayn imetser hot a hust geton.

117
00:06:11,970 --> 00:06:19,400
in etlekhe vokhn arum, khotsh GENSAS, der hot gezogt az &lt;sh-&gt; di letstn mol, mer vet shoyn keyn erk-, ak- dos hot geheysn aktsyes, ot der avekyogn

118
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:21,550
in Ponar, mer vet dos nit zayn,

119
00:06:21,758 --> 00:06:25,025
nor in etlekhe monat arum hot zikh dos ibergekhazert.

120
00:06:25,268 --> 00:06:29,514
nokh dem ey-, a gevise tsayt iz geven ruik. nokh dem hot men gezogt,

121
00:06:29,740 --> 00:06:34,459
nokh dem endikt zikh di gele shaynen; h- zaynen geven bizn draysikstn merts.

122
00:06:34,768 --> 00:06:37,749
un ale hobn moyre gehat, vos vet zayn dem eyn un draysikstn.

123
00:06:38,245 --> 00:06:41,496
nokh dem, got tsu danken, hot men gezogt az me farlengert dos

124
00:06:42,042 --> 00:06:43,352
oyf a monat,

125
00:06:43,543 --> 00:06:44,634
biz APREL'.

126
00:06:45,113 --> 00:06:50,642
ot azoy hot men getsoygn. azoy iz geven, ikh ken aykh nit iber- ibertseyln ale aktsyes vos s'iz geven.

127
00:06:51,053 --> 00:06:52,987
dos iz di, di rafinirte,

128
00:06:53,095 --> 00:06:54,624
der rafinirter mord.

129
00:06:55,035 --> 00:06:56,073
dos iz geven

130
00:06:56,073 --> 00:07:00,873
dos vos me heyst moyshev-zkeynim. dos iz a, a shtub far, eltere mentshn.

131
00:06:59,646 --> 00:07:00,649
far eltern...

132
00:07:00,873 --> 00:07:04,719
hot men, kedey me zol rateven, fun dest vegn, yunge vos kenen arbetn,

133
00:07:04,719 --> 00:07:09,142
hot men &lt;gezogt&gt;, vifl gedarft nemen, hot men tsugenumen ale di altitshke.

134
00:07:09,142 --> 00:07:11,957
an ander mol hot men gezogt az di altitshkes nemt men oyf

135
00:07:11,957 --> 00:07:13,474
mm o- zikh opruen.

136
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:16,366
un a vokh hot men zey gehaltn take in a opru-hoyz.

137
00:07:16,366 --> 00:07:17,912
un m'hot zey gut gekormet.

138
00:07:18,103 --> 00:07:20,172
vayzt oys, hobn zey dos gedarft...

139
00:07:20,432 --> 00:07:25,103
 protestn zaynen nit geven, az, vos me harget yidn. nor vayzt oys hobn zey dos gedarft,

140
00:07:25,103 --> 00:07:28,790
tsi farn Roytn Kreyts, far epe- dos iz geven a propagande.

141
00:07:28,790 --> 00:07:32,114
a vokh hot men zey gehaltn, gekormet, un nokh dem avekgefirt alemen shisn.

142
00:07:32,114 --> 00:07:35,141
un azoy hot dos, azoy hot zikh dos getsoygn. ikh aleyn

143
00:07:35,856 --> 00:07:37,672
bin avek arbetn oykh.

144
00:07:40,986 --> 00:07:47,730
ikh ho- ikh hob gehat a familye-mitglids-oysshr-, -oysvayz. dos heyst az ikh bin a familye-mitglid. di shvester hot gearbet.

145
00:07:47,854 --> 00:07:50,025
ikh oykh. bin ikh arayngefaln

146
00:07:50,419 --> 00:07:52,303
oyf gertneray.

147
00:07:52,697 --> 00:07:56,032
di gantse arbet mayne iz bashtanen, shlepn vaser.

148
00:07:56,781 --> 00:08:01,213
es zol nit zayn azoy, s'iz geven nit, nit zeyer interesant.

149
00:08:01,213 --> 00:08:02,279
fleg ikh tseyln

150
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:03,309
vifl emer.

151
00:08:03,309 --> 00:08:05,949
iz tsu mayne fertsn yor, dakht zikh, flegn mir darfn

152
00:08:05,949 --> 00:08:07,603
mm fer- fun

153
00:08:07,603 --> 00:08:12,249
akht un nayntsik biz hundert zeks emer ahin un tsurik shlepn &lt;tsu, der o&gt; gortn iz geven a groyser.

154
00:08:12,492 --> 00:08:15,000
nor az mir flegn poleven, dos flegn,

155
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:18,459
dos iz ven der, der balebos hot gezogt, "oyb ir vet oyfesn a merele

156
00:08:19,090 --> 00:08:21,230
vel ikh, vel ikh gornit zogn.

157
00:08:21,230 --> 00:08:23,736
ober oyb ir vet veln khotsh eyner aroystrogn,

158
00:08:23,736 --> 00:08:25,404
gib ikh aykh iber in GESTAPO."

159
00:08:25,404 --> 00:08:27,701
ober in shtub zaynen geven tsvey hungerike kinder.

160
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:29,607
flegn mir, farshteyt zikh,

161
00:08:29,607 --> 00:08:34,220
trogn a bulve, a merele, vos, ba- dos bay vos mir hobn gearbet.

162
00:08:34,732 --> 00:08:37,067
hobn mir gehat gemakht aza min,

163
00:08:37,067 --> 00:08:38,561
aza min t-,

164
00:08:38,561 --> 00:08:40,594
mm, haldz-tikhl, a shalik,

165
00:08:40,594 --> 00:08:45,610
un hintn iz er geven farneyt. flegt men dortn araynrukn tsvey kleyne bulvetshkes ahin.

166
00:08:45,610 --> 00:08:47,545
do zet zikh nit, do iz oysgebundn.

167
00:08:47,545 --> 00:08:49,228
ober di daytshn hobn dos alts farshtanen.

168
00:08:49,228 --> 00:08:54,026
mir flegn baytn, hot men... es hobn gearbet dortn, mm, polyakn, m- ammeystns polyakn, a bisl litviner.

169
00:08:54,026 --> 00:08:57,575
flegt men baytn di letste, di letste bebekhes vos m'hot gehat,

170
00:08:57,649 --> 00:09:00,174
umgefer oyf mel. vi arayntrogn in geto?

171
00:09:00,535 --> 00:09:02,557
iz, flegt men neyen aza min,

172
00:09:02,557 --> 00:09:04,433
nu, umgefer vi a hemd,

173
00:09:05,513 --> 00:09:06,682
vi untervesh,

174
00:09:06,682 --> 00:09:08,527
ober s'iz geven opgeshtept.

175
00:09:09,023 --> 00:09:12,729
un dur- in, zeyer, geven kleyninke azelkhe

176
00:09:12,735 --> 00:09:15,153
pasikes, un dortn flegt men araynshitn mel.

177
00:09:15,153 --> 00:09:18,300
un azoy vi s'iz geven shmol, flegt zikh dos nit aropfaln ale,

178
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:19,752
un s'flegt blaybn lign.

179
00:09:19,752 --> 00:09:22,478
itster trogt men dos moderne azelkhe, s'iz do

180
00:09:22,478 --> 00:09:25,081
mantlen oysgeshtepte, ts- trogt men dos.

181
00:09:25,385 --> 00:09:30,559
flegt dos, az me flegt bazukhn, flegt dos oyszen vi vareme vesh, a bisl a dike.

182
00:09:31,213 --> 00:09:37,079
ya, ikh hob aykh fargesn tsu zogn az di gantse tsayt hob ikh geshribn dem tog-bukh. ot dos vos ikh zog aykh itster iz alts farshribn.

183
00:09:39,938 --> 00:09:42,682
ot ale tsutrakhtenishes fun dem MURERn,

184
00:09:44,562 --> 00:09:47,408
ale, ale reyd vegn dem,

185
00:09:47,633 --> 00:09:52,892
altsding, vi s'iz geven di ordenung in geto. s'iz geven, umgefer, a sanitar-politsey,

186
00:09:52,915 --> 00:09:55,618
vos flegn darfn zen, tsukukn es zol zayn,

187
00:09:56,690 --> 00:09:57,845
reyn.

188
00:09:57,845 --> 00:10:03,525
fun di, mir flegn krign PFENNIGn tsu, iz geve- zey hobn f- mir flegn krign zeyer veynik batsolt far undzer arbet.

189
00:10:03,525 --> 00:10:08,855
es flegt koym &lt;klign&gt; krign oystsukoyfn di kartelekh, di broyt-kartelekh vos men flegt gebn.

190
00:10:09,418 --> 00:10:12,368
ober fun dest vegn hobn mir gemuzt tsoln

191
00:10:12,368 --> 00:10:14,188
shtayer far di daytshn.

192
00:10:14,228 --> 00:10:18,338
