00:20:24,613 --> 00:20:30,192
un di geto-politsey hot keyn gever nit gehat. gever hot gehat nor Gens un Desler, zayn hilf.

382
00:20:30,283 --> 00:20:33,517
un di, di, di politsey hobn nor gehat sh- shtekelekh.

383
00:20:33,726 --> 00:20:35,559
di partizaner hobn gehat gever.

384
00:20:35,582 --> 00:20:37,314
hot men Vitnbergn...

385
00:20:37,590 --> 00:20:41,196
dos iz alts in bikhl. ikh kh- ikh khazer zikh, ikh khaz- ikh khazer iber.

386
00:20:39,666 --> 00:20:41,820
yo, yo, yo. s'iz gut, s'iz gut.

387
00:20:41,708 --> 00:20:44,503
hot, de-, me hot gehit

388
00:20:45,020 --> 00:20:47,202
Vitnbergn, zaynen geven farshpart,

389
00:20:47,344 --> 00:20:49,463
un di geto-politsey hot gevust az

390
00:20:49,463 --> 00:20:52,927
me tor zikh dortn nit rirn, vayle m- zey, me vet shteln a vidershtand.

391
00:20:52,927 --> 00:20:55,151
un oyb di daytshn veln derhern az in geto shist men,

392
00:20:55,191 --> 00:20:57,032
dan toyg shoyn take nit.

393
00:20:57,032 --> 00:20:59,440
fun dest vegn iz geven a bisl, a kleyne shiseray.

394
00:20:59,440 --> 00:21:01,939
nokh dem iz Vitnberg geven ibergeton als froy

395
00:21:02,426 --> 00:21:06,864
un imetser hot im derzen oyfn &lt;trepes&gt; untern, unter di k- unter di kleyd, di di lange,

396
00:21:06,864 --> 00:21:08,601
zaynen do menerishe hoyzn.

397
00:21:08,893 --> 00:21:10,096
mit eyn vort:

398
00:21:10,096 --> 00:21:12,077
di geto-politsey hot im arestirt.

399
00:21:12,454 --> 00:21:13,742
m'hot im gefirt

400
00:21:13,742 --> 00:21:14,878
ts-, tsu Gensn.

401
00:21:15,863 --> 00:21:19,395
di partizaner hobn, mit, mit gever, mit shiseray

402
00:21:19,395 --> 00:21:20,716
im opgeklapt.

403
00:21:21,432 --> 00:21:25,813
un m'hot im, un m'hot zikh farbarikadirt un gezogt, "oyb ir vet tsugeyn, shisn mir aykh."

404
00:21:26,106 --> 00:21:30,598
un fun dest vegn hot Vitnberg aleyn bashlosn az er vet geyn.

405
00:21:30,949 --> 00:21:35,347
er zogt, "ikh vil nit zayn di sibe fun umkum fun tsvey un tsvantsik toyznt mentshn.

406
00:21:35,522 --> 00:21:36,194
e-

407
00:21:36,194 --> 00:21:42,266
nu, di, a- m'vet likvidirn, nor efsher vet men nokh nit morgn likvidirn," vi er hot gezogt, oybe er vet nit geyn, iz morgn nayn in der fri.

408
00:21:42,795 --> 00:21:45,627
"efsher vet khot- nokh imetser bavayzn aroysgeyn

409
00:21:45,627 --> 00:21:48,782
in, tsu di partizaner in vald. efsher vet imetser gefinen nokh,

410
00:21:48,782 --> 00:21:53,525
 kh- litviner oder polyakn velkhe veln rateven khotsh m- khotsh tsen, khotsh tsvantsik.

411
00:21:53,525 --> 00:21:55,684
ikh vil nit zayn di sibe." un er hot zikh aleyn,

412
00:21:55,684 --> 00:21:57,352
er iz aleyn avek tsu Gensn.

413
00:21:57,223 --> 00:21:58,989
un vos iz geshen mit im?

414
00:22:00,075 --> 00:22:08,104
 me zogt az Gens hot im gegebn, tsyankali, dos iz di, zikh opsamen, az oyb m'vet im in Gestapo zeyer matern, zol er zikh opsamen.

415
00:22:08,104 --> 00:22:11,071
ikh veys nit tsi dos iz emes. ikh veys nit tsi dos iz,

416
00:22:11,162 --> 00:22:13,552
 tsi dos iz az,

417
00:22:14,250 --> 00:22:16,707
tsi er hot bavizn mit dem zikh tsu banutsn.

418
00:22:17,119 --> 00:22:19,028
nor,

419
00:22:19,028 --> 00:22:23,104
in Gestapo gufe hobn oykh gearbet yidn. dos heyst, zey hobn geramt dortn,

420
00:22:23,515 --> 00:22:29,902
 zey hobn gezen vi m'hot im aroysgetrogn als mes. er iz geven, shreklekh tseharget. m'hot im koym derkent.

421
00:22:29,902 --> 00:22:31,448
farshteyt zikh, er iz umgekumen.

422
00:22:32,762 --> 00:22:34,241
in mayn tog-bukh,

423
00:22:34,686 --> 00:22:36,471
ikh b-, mir zaynen aroys in der fri.

424
00:22:36,471 --> 00:22:40,299
mir hobn gevu- mir hobn n- nit gevust vos. mir zaynen aroys in der fri tsu der arbet

425
00:22:40,305 --> 00:22:44,571
un s'iz zeyer shreklekh. ir farshteyt? mir iz shoyn geven, n- nu, zogn mir shoyn, kimat zekhtsn yor.

426
00:22:44,571 --> 00:22:46,495
ikh bin shoyn geven a dervaksener mentsh.

427
00:22:46,495 --> 00:22:49,811
bay mir iz keyn yugnt nit geven. ikh bin fun kindheyt, fun fertsn,

428
00:22:49,811 --> 00:22:51,368
glaykh gevorn an alte,

429
00:22:51,368 --> 00:22:54,761
vayle,... un s'iz geven di farantvortlekhkeyt far di kleyne,

430
00:22:54,868 --> 00:22:58,473
un s'iz geven zeyer shreklekh az mir &lt;veln&gt; kumen fun der arbet un mir kenen zey nit gefinen.

431
00:22:59,526 --> 00:23:03,278
iz zayn- mir zaynen gekumen fun der arbet, hobn mir zikh dervust vos do iz geven. heyst es, az

432
00:23:03,278 --> 00:23:05,224
mir hobn zikh dervust az Vitnberg iz avek,

433
00:23:06,681 --> 00:23:09,290
un in tog-bukh iz bay mir do aza oyfshrift:

434
00:23:09,955 --> 00:23:11,754
"ikh veys nit vifl ikh vel lebn.

435
00:23:12,216 --> 00:23:13,897
nor vifl ikh zol nit lebn,

436
00:23:14,899 --> 00:23:15,838
iz,

437
00:23:16,249 --> 00:23:17,137
hob ikh,

438
00:23:17,211 --> 00:23:18,504
derfar bin ikh

439
00:23:18,679 --> 00:23:20,380
dankbar Vitnbergn.

440
00:23:20,380 --> 00:23:23,173
haynt hot er mir geratevet. nit nor mir, di mamen,

441
00:23:23,173 --> 00:23:24,017
Miren,

442
00:23:24,017 --> 00:23:25,035
di kinder."

443
00:23:26,728 --> 00:23:33,567
ikh aktsentir di fraze, vayle nokh dem az ikh'l aykh dertseyln mit vos far a tsores, mit vos far a grine gal

444
00:23:33,567 --> 00:23:35,227
es iz gegangen mayn bukh,

445
00:23:35,139 --> 00:23:35,902
aha.

446
00:23:36,533 --> 00:23:40,643
hot men nit gelozn mir afile di, ot di fraze hot men geheysn, ikh zol oysmekn.

447
00:23:40,643 --> 00:23:42,264
ikh'l ay-... dos iz, dos iz shpeter.

448
00:23:44,363 --> 00:23:46,044
azoy hot zikh dertsoygn

449
00:23:47,670 --> 00:23:50,904
biz, es iz shoyn, shoyn gevorn zumer dray un fertsik.

450
00:23:52,412 --> 00:23:56,996
m'hot aribergehoybn ergets, MURERn. s'iz gekumen KITTEL.

451
00:23:57,728 --> 00:24:00,219
KITTEL, dos iz a gevezener artist.

452
00:24:01,288 --> 00:24:02,550
agev, vider,

453
00:24:02,550 --> 00:24:07,259
in bukh iz bay mir ongeshribn, az me zogt er iz a gevezener artist, un aza min

454
00:24:07,259 --> 00:24:08,255
sheyne,

455
00:24:08,255 --> 00:24:14,108
 zayne, arbet hot er, f- farbitn als, als, tsu vern a henker.

456
00:24:14,417 --> 00:24:17,696
az kh- kh'hob g- kh'hob aroysgelozn dem bukh in dray un zekhtsikstn yor,

457
00:24:17,696 --> 00:24:22,699
hob ikh nit gekent dervayzn az er i-... zogn zey, "fun vanet veyst ir az er iz a artist?" zog ikh, "ikh veys nit, m'hot geredt."

458
00:24:22,699 --> 00:24:24,714
er hot dokh mir zayne dokumentn nit gevizn.

459
00:24:24,714 --> 00:24:28,923
hob ikh gemuzt dos oysmekn. un nokh dem hot men gefunen dokumentn; in di shpeterdike iz do.

460
00:24:29,352 --> 00:24:33,261
KIT- KI- mir hobn gevust az KITTEL hot a tsunemenish, likvidator,

461
00:24:33,418 --> 00:24:34,933
az er likvidirt.

462
00:24:34,933 --> 00:24:37,085
un mir hobn farshtanen, er't likvidirn di geto.

463
00:24:37,384 --> 00:24:39,318
nor vayzt oys, hot zey Gens,

464
00:24:39,645 --> 00:24:44,948
khotsh er hot oysgefilt zeyere bafeln, er hot zey, vayzt oys, geshtert. m'hot im aroysgerufn in Gestapo un m'hot im geshosn.

465
00:24:45,147 --> 00:24:46,930
s'iz geven dray un fertsik?

466
00:24:46,429 --> 00:24:50,321
dos iz shoyn geven herbst dray un fertsik. onheyb herbst dray un fertsik.

467
00:24:50,715 --> 00:24:51,479
un,

468
00:24:51,479 --> 00:24:53,108
vi ikh shrayb in tog-bukh,

469
00:24:53,108 --> 00:24:56,750
az di g- di geto hot men farmakht. m'hot shoyn mer nit aroysgelozn oyf der arbet.

470
00:24:57,448 --> 00:25:01,301
az di geto hot shoyn oysgezen vi a mashin, vos arbet nit,

471
00:25:00,823 --> 00:25:01,649
ye.

472
00:25:01,301 --> 00:25:04,023
vos shteyt, un di redelekh faln shoyn fun ir.

473
00:25:06,949 --> 00:25:12,680
un di lets- t- n- di shvester mayne, Mire, hot gelungen, nokh eyder m'hot farmakht di geto, aroysgeyn.

474
00:25:12,973 --> 00:25:15,667
zi hot zikh derredt mit, dortn gefunen

475
00:25:15,724 --> 00:25:16,966
bakante.

476
00:25:17,935 --> 00:25:19,995
 dos iz a bazunderer epizod. ikh,

477
00:25:19,995 --> 00:25:23,717
 azoy vi ikh reyd itster vegn ir, vel ikh dertseyln a bisele ir historye.

478
00:25:24,465 --> 00:25:27,415
 yidn hobn gearbet in dem shtot-arkhiv,

479
00:25:27,415 --> 00:25:28,968
m'hot gemakht dortn a remont,

480
00:25:28,968 --> 00:25:31,024
vu es lign dokumentn.

481
00:25:31,620 --> 00:25:33,554
der direktor fun shtot-arkhiv

482
00:25:34,337 --> 00:25:35,731
hot gezogt,

483
00:25:36,548 --> 00:25:39,832
"veyst vos?" zogt er. "do iz dortn a langer, langer koridor.

484
00:25:40,159 --> 00:25:41,874
lomir optsoymen a shtik.

485
00:25:42,032 --> 00:25:44,236
dos vet in ergets nit zayn fiksirt,

486
00:25:44,496 --> 00:25:46,312
az dos felt a shtik koridor.

487
00:25:46,453 --> 00:25:48,522
un tomer es zol zayn zeyer shlekht,

488
00:25:48,580 --> 00:25:50,329
un m'vet hals- haltn in geto

489
00:25:50,470 --> 00:25:51,797
baym likvidirn,

490
00:25:52,900 --> 00:25:54,027
kumt tsu geyn,

491
00:25:54,027 --> 00:25:55,722
un mir veln aykh do bahaltn."

492
00:25:57,270 --> 00:26:00,740
es iz geven tsugegreyt gants gut. der arkhiv

493
00:26:01,017 --> 00:26:03,643
geyt a-, geyt aroys oyf eyn gas

494
00:26:04,476 --> 00:26:06,326
un fun der zayt iz a kloyster.

495
00:26:07,193 --> 00:26:09,584
der galekh fun kloyster hot oykh geholfn.

496
00:26:10,163 --> 00:26:14,646
un der galekh hot gekrogn a derloybenish tsu makhn a tsveyte tir,

497
00:26:14,668 --> 00:26:16,538
velkhe geyt aroys oyfn hoyf

498
00:26:16,538 --> 00:26:19,189
fun dem arkhiv. far vos hot er dos gedarft?

499
00:26:19,189 --> 00:26:22,866
vayle oybe a mentsh vet arayngeyn fun shtot dortn in hoyf,

500
00:26:22,866 --> 00:26:24,146
di shkheynim veln zen

501
00:26:24,169 --> 00:26:27,572
tsu vemen er iz gegangen, far vos iz er tsurik nit aroysgegangen,

502
00:26:27,612 --> 00:26:30,711
un oyb er vet arayngeyn in der fintster fun kloyster,

503
00:26:30,885 --> 00:26:32,330
vet men im nit zen.

504
00:26:32,556 --> 00:26:36,110
deriber hot er dos gemakht az, nu, kloymersht spetsyel.

505
00:26:36,133 --> 00:26:41,116
er hot gezogt az men darf dos, tomer vet zayn in kloyster a sreyfe un ale veln loyfn durkh di tir,

506
00:26:41,116 --> 00:26:43,333
zol zayn nokh eyner, aroysgang.

507
00:26:44,554 --> 00:26:49,003
un dortn hot men oysge- hot men oysbahaltn nayn monat. zaynen dortn gezesn fertsn yidn.

508
00:26:50,663 --> 00:26:56,563
 zey hobn alts fun zikh oysgeton kedey me zol kenen farkoyfn un kedey me zol kenen dos, lebn.

509
00:26:56,957 --> 00:27:01,186
 a- bay nakht flegt men tsu eynem aroyslozn zikh opvashn.

510
00:27:01,885 --> 00:27:06,486
un tsvishn zey iz geven mayn shvester Mire, un azoy iz zi geblibn lebn fun herbst

511
00:27:06,559 --> 00:27:09,101
fir un fertsik bizn tsvelftn yuli,

512
00:27:09,428 --> 00:27:11,649
 f- f-, herbst dray un fertsik

513
00:27:11,672 --> 00:27:17,060
bizn, tsvelftn yuli fir un fertsik, ven m'hot Vilne bafrayt. dan iz zi aroysgegangen.

514
00:27:17,393 --> 00:27:22,601
zi lebt biz itster, hot tsvey kinder, hot eyniklekh, got tsu danken, lebt in M- Meml,

515
00:27:22,793 --> 00:27:27,253
KLAIPĖDA. nu, a tragedye, s'iz dertrunken gevorn ir man. zi hot aleyn gehodevet di kinder.

516
00:27:27,253 --> 00:27:29,438
nor dos iz shoyn umglikn fun,

517
00:27:29,438 --> 00:27:32,627
fun nokhmilkhomedike tsaytn. dos pasirt in lebn,

518
00:27:29,722 --> 00:27:30,722
fun lebn.

519
00:27:32,627 --> 00:27:33,839
tsum badoyern.

520
00:27:35,582 --> 00:27:39,544
ikh ker zikh tsurik in geto. mir zaynen fun geto nit aroys

521
00:27:40,427 --> 00:27:42,631
un dem dray un tsvantsikstn september,

522
00:27:43,262 --> 00:27:44,471
dray un fertsik,

523
00:27:45,439 --> 00:27:47,238
iz gekumen,

524
00:27:48,004 --> 00:27:51,865
ye, Desler iz antlofn. az Desler iz geven anshtot Gensn, vemen m'hot im dershosn,

525
00:27:50,747 --> 00:27:51,747
ye.

526
00:27:51,865 --> 00:27:55,035
iz gekumen Oberhart, oykh fun di yidishe pney,

527
00:27:55,918 --> 00:27:58,831
 az me zol im, oyfneyen di di,

528
00:27:58,939 --> 00:28:03,438
az me zol im oyfneyen der pasik, az itster iz er der politsey-shef, der geto-forshteyer.

529
00:28:02,359 --> 00:28:02,861
yo.

530
00:28:04,356 --> 00:28:05,835
un s'iz geven umruik.

531
00:28:06,803 --> 00:28:12,157
un nokh dem hot men genumen, di geto-politsey iz arumgegangen... di geto iz dokh a kleyninke, kleyn vi a genets...

532
00:28:12,157 --> 00:28:14,086
d-, iber di etlekhe geselekh,

533
00:28:14,278 --> 00:28:19,309
un gemoldn az ale zoln tsu nayn in der fri loyfn... keyn te- keyn zeyger hobn mir bemeyle nit gehat...

534
00:28:19,392 --> 00:28:22,119
l- in, kumen in hoyf fun yudnrat

535
00:28:22,260 --> 00:28:23,823
far a vikhtike meldung.

536
00:28:24,268 --> 00:28:25,949
ikh bin avekgelofn oykh.

537
00:28:26,918 --> 00:28:28,127
un dortn,

538
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:32,447
 oyf di trepelekh vos iz gegangen tsu Gens' dire...

539
00:28:33,027 --> 00:28:35,603
di trepelekh iz do, di dire iz do;

540
00:28:35,997 --> 00:28:37,900
yedn yor, az ikh kum in Vilne,

541
00:28:37,900 --> 00:28:39,349
makh ikh durkh di veg...

542
00:28:40,401 --> 00:28:42,555
mitn rupor hot men gemoldn,

543
00:28:43,152 --> 00:28:44,698
in daytsh,

544
00:28:45,362 --> 00:28:50,671
az di aynvoyner fun Vilner geto, velkhe zaynen do geku- geven farmakht mit tsvey yor tsurik,

545
00:28:50,863 --> 00:28:55,045
vern aribergefirt in tsvey arbets-lagern: eyne, do gufe in Lite,

546
00:28:55,045 --> 00:28:56,741
lebn Shavl, ŠIAULIAI,

547
00:28:56,741 --> 00:28:57,787
un eyne

548
00:28:57,787 --> 00:28:59,092
in Letland.

549
00:29:00,229 --> 00:29:04,259
 ts- nokh dem hot men tsvey mol ib- i- DA, un az zey, zey ratn undz

550
00:29:04,259 --> 00:29:05,913
az mir zoln mitnemen mit zikh

551
00:29:05,913 --> 00:29:10,560
vareme zakhn, az mir zoln mitnemen dortn tep, emers, ver vos hot,

552
00:29:10,560 --> 00:29:13,064
vayle in di naye lagern vet men dos undz nit gebn.

553
00:29:13,105 --> 00:29:15,827
nokh dem hot men dos tsvey mol ibergekhazert in yidish,

554
00:29:15,827 --> 00:29:18,527
un gezogt az tsu elf a zeyger darfn ale zayn

555
00:29:18,527 --> 00:29:22,313
shoyn bay di, bay Rudnitske, heyst es, baym, baym aroysgang.

